# Per-style preview thumbnails (sc-13135): 128×128 samples, one per catalog style id, shown in the
# Style picker. Generated by scripts/generate-style-thumbnails.mjs and COMMITTED as a bundled asset
# so the thumbnails appear for everyone. To refresh: run `npm run gen:style-thumbnails` (optionally
# `--force`) and commit the updated PNGs. (No ignore rule — the .png files are tracked.)
